                  // 鍏煎鏂版棫鏍煎紡锛氭柊鏍煎紡鐢?ref.text锛屾棫鏍煎紡鎷兼帴 title+content
                  const displayText = ref.text || [ref.title, ref.content, ref.tags].filter(Boolean).join('\n')
